></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns information about the type signature of `declName`. It contains information about which arguments\nare proofs or instances. Returns `none` if no arguments are proofs or instances.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/ProofInstInfo.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.getProofInstInfo?","kind":"def","line":59,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.getProofInstInfo?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/ProofInstInfo.lean#L59-L69"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/ProofInstInfo.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.mkProofInstInfo?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkProofInstInfo?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.ProofInstInfo\">ProofInstInfo</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Analyzes the type signature of `declName` and returns information about which arguments\nare proofs or instances. Returns `none` if no arguments are proofs or instances.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/ProofInstInfo.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.mkProofInstInfo?","kind":"def","line":50,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.mkProofInstInfo?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/ProofInstInfo.lean#L50-L57"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/ProofInstInfo.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.mkProofInst